---
---
<section class="features" id="features">
    <div class="container">
        
        <!-- Feature 1: Family Tree (Creative) -->
        <div class="feature-block fade-up">
            <div class="feature-text centered">
                <span class="badge-pill mb-2">رعاية متكاملة</span>
                <h2>صحة عائلتك.. بيدك</h2>
                <p>لم تعد بحاجة لحمل أوراق التحاليل والوصفات لكل فرد. أنشئ ملفات لأطفالك، والديك، وشريك حياتك، وتابع صحتهم لحظة بلحظة.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-visual family-visual">
                <!-- SVG Connector Lines (Absolute behind) -->
                <svg class="connectors" width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 800 500" preserveAspectRatio="none">
                    <!-- Path from Center Phone to Left Avatar -->
                    <path d="M400,250 C300,250 200,150 150,150" fill="none" stroke="#EAE0D5" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="5,5" />
                     <!-- Path from Center Phone to Right Avatar -->
                    <path d="M400,250 C500,250 600,350 650,350" fill="none" stroke="#EAE0D5" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="5,5" />
                </svg>

                <!-- Center Phone -->
                <div class="phone-center z-10">
                    <img src="/images/screenshots/s6.webp" alt="Family Management" class="screen-img shadow-strong" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
                </div>

                <!-- Floating Avatar Left -->
                <div class="avatar-card pos-left float-slow">
                    <div class="av-img kid"></div>
                    <div class="av-info">
                        <strong>زين (5 سنوات)</strong>
                        <span class="tag-alert">موعد لقاح قريباً</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Floating Avatar Right -->
                <div class="avatar-card pos-right float-reverse">
                    <div class="av-img grandpa"></div>
                    <div class="av-info">
                        <strong>الجد أبو مازن</strong>
                        <span class="tag-success">الضغط: منتظم ✅</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2: Map & Search (Creative) -->
        <div class="feature-split reverse mt-huge fade-up">
            <div class="text-side">
                <span class="badge-pill">بحث ذكي</span>
                <h2>أقرب طبيب إليك</h2>
                <p>لا تضيع وقتك في البحث العشوائي. ابحث حسب الاختصاص، الموقع، أو التقييم. شاهد العيادات القريبة منك على الخريطة واحجز الأنسب.</p>
                
                <ul class="check-list">
                    <li>📍 خرائط دقيقة للعيادات</li>
                    <li>⭐ تقييمات حقيقية من المرضى</li>
                    <li>👨‍⚕️ فلترة حسب الاختصاص والتأمين</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="visual-side map-container">
                <div class="phone-tilted">
                    <img src="/images/screenshots/s8.webp" alt="Map Search" class="screen-img" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
                </div>
                
                <!-- Floating Map Pins -->
                <div class="map-pin pin-1 pop-in">
                    <div class="pin-head">🦷</div>
                    <div class="pin-pulse"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="map-pin pin-2 pop-in delay-1">
                    <div class="pin-head">🩺</div>
                    <div class="pin-pulse"></div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Location Card -->
                <div class="location-card">
                    <div class="loc-icon">🏥</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>عيادة د. سمير</strong>
                        <span>تبعد 1.2 كم • مفتوح</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

           <!-- Feature 3: Records (Classic Clean) -->
           <div class="feature-split mt-huge fade-up">
            <div class="text-side">
                <span class="badge-pill">السجل الطبي</span>
                <h2>تقاريرك.. محفوظة وموثقة</h2>
                <p>وداعاً لضياع صور الأشعة والوصفات الورقية. DocSera يؤرشف كل زيارة، كل تشخيص، وكل دواء في سجل زمني منظم يسهل الرجوع إليه.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="visual-side">
                <div class="phone-upright">
                    <img src="/images/screenshots/s7.webp" alt="Medical Reports" class="screen-img shadow-strong" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
                </div>
                <!-- Document Decoration -->
                <div class="doc-deco doc-1">📃 وصفة</div>
                <div class="doc-deco doc-2">🧬 تحليل</div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .features {
        padding: 100px 0;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #FFFFFF 0%, #FAFAFA 100%);
        overflow: hidden; /* For absolute elements */
    }

    .mt-huge { margin-top: 150px; }
    .mb-2 { margin-bottom: 20px; }

    .centered { text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 60px; }

    .badge-pill {
        background: var(--c-sand-light);
        color: var(--c-main-dark);
        padding: 6px 16px;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: var(--c-text);
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    
    p {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        color: var(--c-text-muted);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* Family Visual Scene */
    .family-visual {
        position: relative;
        height: 600px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .connectors {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0; left: 0;
        z-index: 0;
        opacity: 0.6;
    }

    .phone-center {
        width: 280px;
        z-index: 5;
        position: relative;
    }
    .shadow-strong {
        box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        border-radius: 40px;
        border: 8px solid white;
    }

    .avatar-card {
        position: absolute;
        background: white;
        padding: 12px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        min-width: 200px;
        z-index: 6;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .av-img { width: 45px; height: 45px; border-radius: 50%; background-size: cover; background-color: #eee; }
    .kid { background-image: url('https://api.dicebear.com/7.x/avataaars/svg?seed=Felix'); }
    .grandpa { background-image: url('https://api.dicebear.com/7.x/avataaars/svg?seed=Aneka'); }

    .av-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; text-align: right; }
    .av-info strong { font-size: 0.9rem; }
    
    .tag-alert { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #E67E22; background: #FFF3E0; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 2px; }
    .tag-success { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #27AE60; background: #E8F8F5; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 2px; }

    .pos-left { top: 20%; left: 10%; }
    .pos-right { bottom: 25%; right: 10%; }

    /* Split Layout */
    .feature-split {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 80px;
    }
    .feature-split.reverse { flex-direction: row-reverse; }

    .text-side { flex: 1; }
    .check-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-top: 24px; }
    .check-list li { margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--c-text); font-size: 1.05rem; }

    .visual-side {
        flex: 1;
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .phone-tilted {
        width: 270px;
        transform: rotate(-5deg);
        transition: transform 0.5s;
        border-radius: 40px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        border: 6px solid white;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .map-container:hover .phone-tilted { transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1.02); }

    /* Map Pins */
    .map-pin {
        position: absolute;
        z-index: 10;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .pin-head {
        width: 40px; height: 40px;
        background: var(--c-main);
        color: white;
        border-radius: 50% 50% 0 50%;
        transform: rotate(45deg);
        display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 144, 146, 0.4);
        border: 2px solid white;
    }
    .pin-head::after {
        content: attr(data-icon);
        transform: rotate(-45deg); /* Counter rotate icon */
        font-size: 18px;
    }
    
    .pin-1 { top: 10%; right: 20%; animation: bounce 2s infinite; }
    .pin-2 { bottom: 30%; left: 15%; animation: bounce 2.5s infinite reverse; }

    .location-card {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 50px; right: -20px;
        background: white;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        z-index: 11;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .loc-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; }

    /* Doc Deco */
    .doc-deco {
        position: absolute;
        background: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--c-text-muted);
        border: 1px solid #EEE;
        z-index: 0;
    }
    .doc-1 { top: 100px; left: 20px; transform: rotate(-10deg); }
    .doc-2 { bottom: 100px; right: 20px; transform: rotate(10deg); }
    .phone-upright { position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 260px; border-radius: 40px; border: 6px solid white; box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }

    @keyframes bounce {
        0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
        50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    }

    /* Pop In Animation */
    .pop-in { animation: popIn 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) forwards; opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.5); }
    .visible .pop-in { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .feature-split { flex-direction: column !important; gap: 40px; text-align: center; }
        .family-visual { height: 400px; }
        .connectors { display: none; }
        .pos-left { left: 0; top: 10%; }
        .pos-right { right: 0; bottom: 10%; }
        .phone-center { width: 220px; }
        
        .map-pin { display: none; } /* Hide complex decorative elements on mobile */
    }
</style>
